  <description>
    <p>
      A local 2-player spaceship asteroid survival game. Each game round lasts 120 seconds. 
      The top shooter wins. Easy-mode keeps your power-ups when hit by an asteroid. 
      Gamepads are supported, but same keyboard playing is more fun!
    </p>
